description:
Anna Graves performs "Made To Love Someone" live at The Current
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Minnesota-born singer-songwriter Anna Graves has spent time in Los Angeles and in Nashville, but it's in Minnesota that she feels the most connection. "It's really a place where I draw a lot of inspiration," Graves told The Local Show host Diane during a June 2025 interview. While making that visit to The Current, Anna Graves stopped in to our studio to record solo acoustic versions of three songs, including an unreleased song that speaks to Graves' Minnesota roots. Watch a performance of "Made To Love Someone" above.
